title: NFL Week 11 Fantasy Advice with Heath Cummings (Football 11/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings to break down the Week 10 slate from a fantasy perspective. The guys take a look at Thursday Night Football between the Packers and Seahawks (1:35), what quarterbacks you should stream this week (12:00), concerns about Tom Brady (16:35), Nick Chubb vs. Sony Michel (19:55), the Titans running back situation (22:45), David Johnson's potential down the stretch (24:00) and guys to stash for the playoffs (29:30).
